::  Multi-field named-cast — +$ nona-shape then ^- nona-shape (STOA176).
::  Peek budget field_count+3 after named_cast_parts widen.
+$  nona-shape
  $:  from=@u32
      amount=@u32
      fee=@u32
      nonce=@u32
      memo=@u32
      tag=@u32
      to=@u32
      via=@u32
      ref=@u32
  ==
^-  nona-shape
